50|$|Wacko is a 1983 arcade game by Bally Midway. It {{featured}} a unique angled, or sloped, cabinet design and {{a combination of}} trackball and <b>joystick</b> <b>controls.</b> The main character also appears in Kozmik Krooz'r.|$|R
